{"tid":2058770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［以正視聽］對家係咁吹大風，叫班後生讓步重新出發","createTime":"2020-06-10T12:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T13:39:48.000Z","uid":116198,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"32ebfda9fc599b2abbfeb9d05267bed032e95fd2","tid":2058770,"uid":116198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:08:43.000Z","msg":"而家一周年好多媒體吹風向，<br />\n訪問受傷黑警之類，總之搵人扮中立，<br />\n講兩邊一人讓一步、話班後生洗腦、<br />\n扮可憐、叫人重新出發。<br />\n<br />\n我想問大家，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家有冇一個港共高官受到懲罰？！<br />\n<br />\n我只見到夠紅唔駛有能力既，升官發財，<br />\n仲不斷用行政手段，各種途徑打壓自由。<br />\n<br />\n紅底法官、律政司，視法治為無物，加你控罪，判最高刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n黑警繼續高調無故拘捕，藍絲繼續作威作福。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁叫讓步？！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人無恥則無敵</span>"},{"pid":"acb6a113c0a0d34f4f546505e1b88a531dcb99bc","tid":2058770,"uid":231583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:09:39.000Z","msg":"似乎想搵班人玩中間路線唔好再分藍黃，緩和社會氣氛"},{"pid":"991cc5dce1e3d3eac1c1965ec70f40469c4e9f3b","tid":2058770,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"有冇一個黑警狗官比人懲罰？<br />\n升職就有<br />\n<br />\n手足死既死，比人砌生豬肉<br />\n和？<br />\n對得住周同學，陳同學？"},{"pid":"b8eb0ff7c115c1f8a46afaf2ecc9756278c30b9e","tid":2058770,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:15:00.000Z","msg":"跟住會大量利誘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33aee90462f1b51946230f14c21031bac9c9fc95","tid":2058770,"uid":8500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:18:44.000Z","msg":"之前話會開多d鐵飯碗位<br />\n又少一堆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86811a5badf3521426460f9ea7c28d9820b9265c","tid":2058770,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"緩你老母和<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"553b4f396de90ccda944843dfd3160c5b9b42e85","tid":2058770,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:21:40.000Z","msg":"唔好激嬲中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c605d838843dcc08dc8b836f35340980216569","tid":2058770,"uid":47202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"班死黑警同港共既仇係一世，如果有來世就直到佢哋個個哂落地獄為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果我哋有絲毫既退讓，我地點面對死去或被捕既手足。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可，香港獨立，唯一出路。<br />\n如果他朝香港有獨立既一日，呢一班仆街都要上斷頭台。"},{"pid":"7bd1bde08b8082e1964abec5e5b13b6e8cbcdb2c","tid":2058770,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:25:55.000Z","msg":"嗰啲訪問唔係都係大公文匯屈文妓寫？"},{"pid":"d6aacbb7093fb9f71c2e5e0467932562d42af418","tid":2058770,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:27:01.000Z","msg":"我啲兄弟唔會原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7981755a14b60769c27cf84ee40e08b5bdae5a66","tid":2058770,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840203dd2dc5f0d7cea47a60b5faedf59d7793cf","tid":2058770,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4347c47fec6e2f6c117016f108cf7e1e8e8d012e","tid":2058770,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:35:50.000Z","msg":"明明步步進逼嘅係個政府<br />\n真係做雞都要攞貞節牌坊"},{"pid":"2b24338e4a9381dc9d3b29a0dbef7b2d3cc80112","tid":2058770,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:38:09.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可 <br />\n<br />\n如果這樣就退讓 是否連自己的自由都退讓 <br />\n我們要最先救在生的人 ，以乘繼義士遺志。"},{"pid":"4916fe01e633fb21b719b0875bdfb82517220b53","tid":2058770,"uid":355748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:41:32.000Z","msg":"班離地人士活喺夢中<br />\n個社會去到咁嘅地步唔係你死就我亡<br />\n仲想返到以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d00767a24f61cd419fda73e63c444a27f3b3979","tid":2058770,"uid":147823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"受害要得到賠償, 加害要得到懲罰, 有人要做協調."},{"pid":"06bd5954a8b292fd42186f405fe88ed5c0bbcc3b","tid":2058770,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"舊年6月9無認受嘅港共政權如果讓步撤回，真係可以重新出發再呃多香港人十幾年嘅，但612、721、831、暴力攻打中大理大之後，有嘅只係血海深仇。港共仲on99發夢從教育著手洗下一代腦，諗吓呢代個家長每日教D仔女反共，共产党係未來100年都無可能管治香港"},{"pid":"2eaa7caa8b9eee32c4344f6d1792be7a928bf0d4","tid":2058770,"uid":146621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"acb6a113c0a0d34f4f546505e1b88a531dcb99bc","tid":2058770,"uid":231583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:09:39.000Z","msg":"似乎想搵班人玩中間路線唔好再分藍黃，緩和社會氣氛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:54:22.000Z","msg":"上年早d撤回就唔會有警暴問題<br />\n早d肯查警暴就唔會黃藍對立得咁犀利<br />\n而家先行中間路線真係on99"},{"pid":"da85b90e0801d32ac28613ff24b404995260fc06","tid":2058770,"uid":1339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:57:14.000Z","msg":"我要警隊賠返咁多條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以命換命"},{"pid":"ac8a668a5d7b9c0ab81c91ffecbf433f9542122f","tid":2058770,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb6a113c0a0d34f4f546505e1b88a531dcb99bc","tid":2058770,"uid":231583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:09:39.000Z","msg":"似乎想搵班人玩中間路線唔好再分藍黃，緩和社會氣氛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:59:00.000Z","msg":"小心田生同佢啲fd"},{"pid":"1f183292b39631783a5d4d4f94996e02029df92